item.title: By: Phil Mac Giolla Bhain
item.dc:creator: Phil Mac Giolla Bhain
item.description: Hello I am an activist with the NUJ in Ireland. I am the rep for the New Media Industrial Council. I wish to attend and distribute an NUJ recruitment leaflet specifically aimed at the new media sector. I also,of course, wish to take a full part in the meet. Regards Phil
item.content:encoded:
Hello
I am an activist with the NUJ in Ireland. I am the rep for the New Media Industrial Council.
I wish to attend and distribute an NUJ recruitment leaflet specifically aimed at the new media sector.
I also,of course, wish to take a full part in the meet.
Regards
Phil
